"msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=K7euM6APFEs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DK7euM6APFEs&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y90zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=1b73eae2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=K7euM6APFEs</a><br />\n<br />\n有無人睇過？有好多集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得紅白機好撚勁 一鳩嘢秒晒同期咁多機<br />\n之後任天堂再畀sony收皮<br />\n最撚慘係sega 出親啲機都係黑色 而黑色做主機好似有詛咒咁 好快就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而ps2就打破到黑色主機會好快收皮呢個神話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d509dfe9ba7efb48d9cf78cd69b01443e4b8c9c2","tid":146007,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T02:54:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最失敗嗰部GameCube都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黑歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ngamecube其實好正，wii u先係黑歷史</blockquote><br />\nGC係出錯時間<br />\n前面PS2出左2年佢先出但PS2已經站穩哂<br />\n不過咁都唔算<br />\n死係死在當年XBOX橫空出世佢又要同佢鬥埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2邊夾擊咪仆街"},{"pid":"c102d57aae0fe59357a46264d33254f6b44b4ad5","tid":146007,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:18:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最失敗嗰部GameCube都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黑歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ngamecube其實好正，wii u先係黑歷史</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正解<br />\nWiiU一定比GC失敗<br />\nGC多好撚多第3方獨家game，只係銷量唔太好先downgrade移植到ps2, e.g. Bio 4 and Tales of syphopnia, viewtiful joe<br />\n獨佔又有bio 1 remake 同 bio 0， Baten Kaitos<br />\n又有pso加持<br />\n係一部滿足到hardcore gamer嘅機<br />\n反而WiiU真係唔可以太滿足到hardcore gamer"}]}